  )
  (text "V1.0 - Base template\n\nV2.4 - Added additional filtering and voltage follower before ADC\n\nV2.5 - Fix for redesign of hat and redonoe current sensor\n\nV2.5S - Standardized Version of previous board\n\nV3.0 - Redesign to work as a daughterboard with Peripheral SOM board "
